v0.7.0: elevation split, DO_NOT_SHARE layout, cdb deep analysis, redaction, scope reporting

- Elevation split: unelevated parent, UAC helper only for minidump copy (ElevatedDumpCopy) with staging-path validation, reparse-point re-check, and registry-sourced source path constrained under %SystemRoot%.
- Storage layout: FlareStorage centralizes paths; raw minidumps + cdb transcripts under DO_NOT_SHARE/, user-visible Reports/ holds only the report. One-shot migration from 0.6.x.
- cdb integration: CdbLocator restricted to Microsoft-managed debugger roots (no PATH fallback). CdbRunner drives !analyze -v. CdbAnalysisCache keys per-dump on size+mtime+version.
- Redaction: ReportRedaction scrubs UUID, computer name, %USERPROFILE% / %APPDATA% / OneDrive paths; applied across every user-visible UI surface (log, status bar, tooltips, popups); on by default.
- Scope + collector health: SCOPE block discloses requested window, retention floors, per-collector cap hits, and notices (canary/skipped/failure). Multi-GPU SM-localization suppressed when >1 NVIDIA adapter. ReportAnalysis pairs permissive heuristics with calibrated prose.
- New collectors: SystemInfo (board/BIOS/CPU/RAM), GpuInfo PCIe gen/width + BAR1/ReBAR + multi-GPU, BugcheckCatalog (MDMP/PAGEDUMP/PAGEDU64), Kernel-Power 41 extraction, setupapi.dev.log NVIDIA driver-install parser, NvidiaDriverVersion marketing-form conversion.
- Format-drift canaries: setupapi, cdb, nvlddmkm — surface in the SCOPE block.
- Robustness: regex timeouts, fatal.log rotation, corrupt settings.json quarantined, debounced+atomic settings writes, cancellation threaded through every collector.
- Build-kind label: FlareIsRelease MSBuild flag drives title-bar prefix ([DEV BUILD] / [SNAPSHOT] / clean) and About dialog tag.
- UI: report folder fixed to %LOCALAPPDATA%\FLARE\Reports (input row dropped). UseLayoutRounding + SnapsToDevicePixels default everywhere for crisp 1-DIP hairlines at any DPI.
- Structure: ReportInput record + ReadEvents<T> helper + FlareDependencies test seam.
- CI: SHA-pinned actions, SHA256SUMS.txt, packaged-binary smoke tests. Release body now read from HISTORY.log.
- Docs sweep: ARCHITECTURE/CONTRIBUTING/README updated for DO_NOT_SHARE, redaction, build labels, unsigned-binary stance.
